      "content": "Focus on polished, understated grooming; think neat hair, subtle makeup, and clean nails to project meticulousness. For attire, opt for well-tailored, classic suiting in muted colors—a sharp blazer and crisp shirt speak volumes about your professionalism. Maintaining confident, composed body language, such as good posture and deliberate movements, is also key to appearing authoritative in the room.",
