      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. can u get a bit more specific with the grooming stuff though? like, when you say \"neat hair,\" what does that actually mean in a corporate sense? i have some clients who have different hair textures or styles that they feel might not fit that \"neat\" or \"polished\" look. what should they be aiming for to make sure they don't look unprofessional?",
